items.name: Aureon
items.description: Aureon Technology is a full-service technology provider established in 1994 to provide businesses with solutions for software development and licensing, networking, IT staffing and IT management. By providing a broad range of services, we can offer a suite of solutions that is unrivaled in the region. Technologies that in the past were disparate and fragmented have become interdependent. Web sites rely on databases. Applications rely on wide area networks. And so on. Most technology firms address individual portions of the technology landscape, often creating gaps between areas that need to be tightly knit together. By offering a single-source provider, a company can reduce the complexities associated with coordinating services between multiple providers.

items.name: New Horizons Memphis, Tennessee
items.description:
We empower people to succeed through learning.

New Horizons Central has been serving businesses and individuals in the community for over 32 years. With convenient locations, we offer a wide range of technical, application and business skills courses. As the world of computer technology continues to evolve at light speed, New Horizons helps the world’s workforce stay proficient with the latest technologies and achieve their career goals. It’s what we’ve been doing better than anyone else for years, and what we plan to do well into the future.

What Makes New Horizons Central Unique?

Learn what you want, when you want, & how you want.

As part of the largest independent IT Training Provider, New Horizons Computer Learning Center delivers more courses than any other IT training company. Our various approaches empower students with unprecedented flexibility to tailor their learning schedules and locations by deciding when, where and how they want to learn.

New Horizons has trained employees at all 100 companies listed in Fortune magazine’s ranking of America’s 100 largest corporations and over half of the Global 100. We are ranked in the top 5% of the industry for training quality and customer satisfaction as reported by an independent, third-party learning and quality assurance company, Knowledge Advisors. Training from New Horizons provides measurable results.

items.name: Cenetric, Inc.
items.description:
Cenetric IT Services is a locally owned and operated full service IT provider. Based in Olathe, KS Cenetric services  business and  Nonprofit organizations. Our clients range from small businesses to Fortune 500's, to a locally based Regional restaurant franchise where we support the Corporate Office and restaurants in addition to a variety of other businesses in the Kansas City Metro area. 

Cenetric IT Services specializes in Managed IT Services which allows us to service our clients IT needs into a customized package for their specific business. Our flat monthly fee allows our clients to budget a fixed amount each month for IT services, with Cenetric there are no overages, no hourly rates and no additional costs. We provide unlimited support, both remote help desk support and on-site support. As part of our all in one service we insure that our clients network is secured, backed up and healthy every day. Cenetric IT Services takes a proactive approach to IT services, with the use of our remote agents we are able to remotely monitor a network, identify issues before they become problems and resolve those issues quickly and efficiently with as little inconvenience as possible for our clients. Cenetric IT works with all of our clients as a virtual CIO, helping to plan out expansion, procurement of new hardware and software and future IT costs, we work hard to become a part of our clients business and a trusted advisor. 

For nearly 10 years Cenetric has been a client focused IT Service provider where we live by our company motto- “Our Mission is to Further Your Mission”

items.name: Pendello Solutions, Inc.
items.description:
Pendello is the fastest-growing provider of IT support and services in Kansas City for small and medium-sized businesses.  Why?  We remove obstacles, inefficiencies and frustrations to enrich the businesses and lives of our clients through technology.  

At Pendello, we afford small and medium sized businesses the opportunity to realize the same advantages of large, global enterprises, by leveraging business and technology knowledge to obtain greater efficiency and profitability. To be a leader in today’s fast-paced, global economy, a company must streamline processes, reporting, and operations by utilizing the latest technology to react swiftly, strategically, and unfailingly. Pendello provides companies with the resources to effectively evaluate and support current technology, review existing processes, visualize avenues for improvement, implement vision-driven decision making, and comprehend the available technologies leading to a complete business technology management solution.

items.name: Hanebutt Technologies, Inc.
items.description:
Hanebutt Technologies used to be just another of the typical IT support companies out there. Once, we were just about reactions to IT problems for our clients, showing up to fix computers when they were broken, selling some new products when the old ones just wouldn’t turn back on again. It was just the way of things.

No more, though. Seven years ago, we changed our ownership and leadership, and that meant renewing the way we work with our clients. We want to be more than just the fix-it people now – we want to be your partner. You use your information technology every day, but so many businesses just see it as a boring old tool to get the job done.

We think IT can be more than that.

Today, we focus on the needs of your business before the needs of your technology. The two should go hand-in-hand. When we come to work with you, our first questions aren’t going to be about your computer systems. We want to know who you are and what you want your technology to do for you.

Centriq accepts Microsoft Software Assurance Training Vouchers (SATV’s) as well.
